Interface Engine.EnrollmentCallback

  • Enclosing interface:
    Engine

    public static interface Engine.EnrollmentCallback
    Acquires and returns PreEnrollmentFmd for the purpose of creating enrollment FMD.

    During enrollment CreateEnrollmentFmd() repeatedly calls EnrollmentCallback.GetFmd() to acquire FMDs for enrollment.
